OL,3,CCarer who helped husband play football
OL,4,Cagain after brain injury up for award
OL,6,FShe said: "It's all well and good
OL,7,Fhaving the hospital staff and medical
OL,8,Fprofessionals talking through that
OL,9,Fprocess, but often so much of what
OL,10,Fpeople need is just that person who's
OL,11,Flived it, who can just be gentle and
OL,12,Fsupportive and encouraging.
OL,14,F"Sue does this without even thinking
OL,15,Fabout it, she won't even consider that
OL,16,Fthat's something that she does."
